About Us Welcome to our Lebanon Office. At Peoples Bank you can simplify your life with the ability and convenience to take care of all your financial needs in one place. For more than 110 years, we have embraced the idea that a bank can make a difference in the lives of customers and community members. We are proud of our heritage, loyal to our customers and committed to our communities. Stop by. Our Lebanon Office is conveniently located at 910 Columbus Ave. in Lebanon, OH. You can also visit any one of our other locations throughout Ohio, West Virginia and Kentucky.


Video















Products & Services

Banking

Personal checking, savings, Money market and CDs
Auto Personal, Home equity and Mortgage loans 
Mobile banking, online banking and other convenient services
Business checking, savings, money markets and CDs
Business loans, lines of credit and credit cards 
Business cash management services
Debit Cards, Credit Cards, Prepaid Debit Cards, Gift Cards, MoneyPass® 



Investments

eComprehensive financial planning
Investment Services
In-house 401(k) administration and services
Trust and estate planning



Insurance

Home and Auto Insurance
Life and Health Insurance 
Commercial Insurance 
Group Health and Life Insurance















Manage
We value your time as much as you do, which is why we offer a wide variety of flexible financial solutions to help you manage your banking needs quickly and conveniently.  Learn More




Borrow
Wake up in the home of your dreams or slide into the driver's seat of a new car. Whatever your dreams, a loan from Peoples Bank can make them a reality.  Learn More




Insure
Peoples Insurance Agency at Peoples Bank has access to hundreds of smart insurance solutions, making it easy to shop for quality, affordable insurance coverage. Learn More




Invest
At Peoples Bank, we offer a full range of flexible investment solutions that help you build your investment portfolio. We offer you timely market advice and products and services with competitve returns.  Learn More




Plan
Whatever life-stage you're in, career you hold or dream you're chasing, we're here to help you in every step of the way.  Learn more











