Saluting the Heroes Among Us
To show our appreciation and respect for the sacrifices they make, Peoples Bank has created a banking program for our hometown heroes. This exclusive program is designed specifically for active U.S. military service members and veterans, current and retired law enforcement, firefighters, Emergency Medical Technicians and teachers in our communities.
Peoples Hometown Heroes Banking is our way of saying “thank you” to those who give so much for our community. This special program is an add-on to any Peoples Bank® personal checking account and is loaded with great benefits and features.
 
We Are Pleased to Offer Our Hometown Heroes:

$50 after your first two bills paid using our Bill Pay service1
$50 after your first direct deposit1
Free first order of checks2
Exclusive Hometown Heroes Debit Card

Also Exclusive to You:

Complimentary investment review and analysis from a financial advisor at Peoples Bank3
$250 off loan origination fees on any new Residential Real Estate Loan4
$100 off loan origination fees on any new Personal Loan4
0.50% reduction in rate on any new Personal Loan with auto-debit from a personal checking account with Peoples Bank4
50% off a new Safe Deposit Box (at available locations)5
Complimentary insurance quote6

Add Peoples Hometown Heroes Banking to any personal checking account and start enjoying the benefits today!

GET YOUR HOMETOWN HEROES ACCOUNT TODAY!
1Your account may be eligible for a $50 bonus after your first payroll direct deposit. Additionally, your account may be eligible for a $50 bonus after paying a minimum of two bills through bill pay service.  Cash bonus offers valid for qualified customers opening a new account only.  One offer per customer.  Bill Pay offer valid for 60 days from account opening.  Must pay a minimum of two bills within 60 days of opening a new qualified account.  Direct Deposit offer valid for 60 days from account opening.  Cash bonus will be paid within 60 days of qualifying service.  IRS form 1099 will be issued for all bonuses in excess of $10.  2Offer limited to one box of basic checks.  Postage and shipping fees may apply.  3Peoples Bank and its subsidiaries are independent of Raymond James.  Securities offered exclusively through Raymond James Financial Services Inc., Member NASD/SIPC, an independent broker/dealer, and are NOT FDIC insured or insured by any other government agency.  NOT GUARANTEED by Peoples Bank / Not Deposits / Subject to risk and may lose value.  Trust & Investment Services offered through Peoples Bank: 138 Putnam Street Marietta, Ohio 45750. 40.25% reduction in rate on any new Personal Loan with auto-debit from a personal checking account with Peoples Bank and another 0.25% for being a Hometown Heroes member. Loan offers not limited to one per customer. Loans are subject to credit approval. Personal loan rate discount requires auto debit from a Peoples Bank checking account. This rate offer cannot be combined with any other rate discount. Not valid on Dreams2Keys product.  550% discount only available for first year on new safe deposit box accounts.  Subject to availability.  6Insurance products offered through Peoples Insurance Agency, LLC. Insurance products are: NOT FDIC Insured • NOT GUARANTEED by Peoples Bank • NOT a deposit • NOT insured by a federal government agency • Subject to risk and may lose value.




 
 
  
 
 
 










