News Archive







Personal Service Is Our Focus
	


	Since 1903, The Peoples National Bank of Mt. Pleasant has been a cornerstone of the surrounding communities, furnishing financial services to our neighbors and local businesses for over a century. We are headquartered in the historic village of Mt. Pleasant, Ohio, with branches in Adena and Dillonvale. Mainly serving the tri-county area of Jefferson, Harrison, and Belmont, our customer base extends into neighboring counties in Ohio, West Virginia, and Pennsylvania.

All decisions are made locally by management and directors, people from the local area who understand the needs of our communities. At Peoples National, the Directors, Officers and staff are focused on providing the utmost in personal service to our customers and in promoting the development and financial well-being of the communities the bank serves and has been serving for over 100 years. When you call Peoples National Bank during business hours you will hear a real person who is interested in serving you. Personal service is our most important attribute.












